---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Data Retention Policy | Quantum Code Devs"
  description="Data retention policy for Quantum Code Devs."
>
  <section class="space-y-5">
    <p class="inline-flex rounded-full border border-cyan-200/30 bg-cyan-200/10 px-4 py-1 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-cyan-100">
      Legal
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-white md:text-5xl">Data Retention Policy</h1>
    <p class="max-w-3xl text-lg text-slate-300">
      This policy outlines how long Quantum Code Devs stores data collected through client communication, project delivery, and website interactions.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Last updated: July 16, 2026</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 grid gap-4">
    <article class="glass-card">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Inquiry Data</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-300">
        Contact form submissions and inquiry emails are retained for up to 24 months to support follow-up communication, proposal updates, and service history.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="glass-card">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Project Data</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-300">
        Project records, contracts, invoices, and deliverable documentation are retained for up to 7 years for legal, accounting, and operational continuity requirements.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="glass-card">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Analytics and Logs</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-300">
        Technical logs and website analytics are retained only as long as reasonably needed for performance, security monitoring, and service quality improvements.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="glass-card">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Deletion Requests</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-300">
        You may request deletion of personal data where legally permissible. Some records may be retained where required for tax, legal, or contractual compliance.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="glass-card">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Policy Updates</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-300">
        We may revise this policy periodically. Updated versions will be published on this page with a revised effective date.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>
